{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8f7cc339-b70b-49cf-92f8-99358a6fb656", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8f7cc339-b70b-49cf-92f8-99358a6fb656@1.pkg/1772597685980/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597686984", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8f7cc339-b70b-49cf-92f8-99358a6fb656@1.pkg/1772597685980/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597686984"}, "identifier": "8f7cc339-b70b-49cf-92f8-99358a6fb656", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查理解劳动对个人和社会的价值。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：&ldquo;创新劳动方式&rdquo;说法错误，在材料中并非每一个劳动者都创新了他们的劳动方式，因此这一选项并不正确。故A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：材料并没有提到诚信，更多在强调奋斗的重要性，因此&ldquo;用诚信构建和谐社会生活&rdquo;说法与题意不相符合，故B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：材料中的每一个劳动者都在坚持以自己的平凡劳动创造社会财富，并实现自己的人生价值，因此C选项符合题意。因此C正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：题意是在赞美这些平凡劳动者们兢兢业业通过奋斗创造美好生活的行为，而非赞美他们&ldquo;为追求高薪报酬不懈奋斗&rdquo;，因此D说法错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选C</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）风雨无阻穿梭不停的外卖骑手、敲击键盘激荡脑力的程序员、返乡创业耕耘田野的新农人&hellip;&hellip;在日常生活中，这些普通人以无数微光辉映时代星空，每一个人都是主角。这赞美了他们（　　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）风雨无阻穿梭不停的外卖骑手、敲击键盘激荡脑力的程序员、返乡创业耕耘田野的新农人……在日常生活中，这些普通人以无数微光辉映时代星空，每一个人都是主角。这赞美了他们（　　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8f7cc339-b70b-49cf-92f8-99358a6fb656@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977241802", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>坚持梦想追逐美好的生活，创新劳动方式</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>用诚信构建和谐社会生活，践行社会责任</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>以平凡劳动创造社会财富，实现人生价值</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>为追求高薪报酬不懈奋斗，创造幸福人生</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）风雨无阻穿梭不停的外卖骑手、敲击键盘激荡脑力的程序员、返乡创业耕耘田野的新农人&hellip;&hellip;在日常生活中，这些普通人以无数微光辉映时代星空，每一个人都是主角。这赞美了他们（　　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning